postscript.p:
Remember the word, which ſaith;


                     Look not every man on his own things, but every man alſo on the things of others: Let the ſame mind be in you that was in Chriſt Jeſus, who was moved with compaſſion toward the people, and pronounceth thoſe bleſſed that feed the hungry, cloth the naked, viſit the ſick and ſuch as are in priſon,

                  Phil. 2.4, 5. Mat. 14.14. & 25.34, 35, 36, &c.
